-----------------------------------------
Introduction ::: Introducing the problem:
-----------------------------------------

Our task is to compute the similarity of two pairs of words that occur together within different contexts and in addition study how the effect of a particular
context plays a role in the similarity score.

Goal: to build embedding models that predict the effect context has on the human predicted scores.

This is an unsupervised task, so there will be no training & testing data to perform the validation methods. 



